trans-unit.source: Contains contextual state information for a designer, such as the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller tillståndsinformation om kontextuella för en designer som den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This includes permanent state information, such as the list of services running in the designer.
trans-unit.target: Detta inkluderar tillståndsinformation, till exempel listan över tjänster som körs i designern.

trans-unit.source: It also includes transient state consisting of context items including the set of currently selected objects as well as the editing tool being used to manipulate objects on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Den omfattar också tillfälligt tillstånd som består av kontexten artiklar inklusive uppsättning markerade objekt samt redigeringsverktyg som används för att ändra objekt i designvyn.

trans-unit.source: The EditingContext represents the communication boundary that is shared between the hosting application and the [!INCLUDE[wfd1](~/add/includes/wfd1-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: EditingContext representerar kommunikation gränsen som delas mellan värd och [!INCLUDE[wfd1](~/add/includes/wfd1-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The EditingContext was implemented as a concrete class for ease of use.
trans-unit.target: EditingContext har implementerats som en konkret klass lätt att använda.

trans-unit.source: Override <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.CreateServiceManager%2A> and <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.CreateContextItemManager%2A> to use customized managers derived from <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ServiceManager> and <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ContextItemManager>.
trans-unit.target: Åsidosätt <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.CreateServiceManager%2A>och <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.CreateContextItemManager%2A>använda anpassade chefer som härleds från <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ServiceManager>och <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ContextItemManager>.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ContextItemManager> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ServiceManager> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.CreateContextItemManager%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.CreateServiceManager%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the context item manager that is returned by the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.Items*> property.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en instans av kontexten hanteraren för objektet som returneras av den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.Items*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.Items*>

trans-unit.source: The default implementation creates a <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ContextItemManager> that supports delayed activation of design editor managers through the declaration of a <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.SubscribeContextCallback> attribute on the design editor manager.
trans-unit.target: Standardimplementering skapar en <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ContextItemManager>som stöder den fördröjda aktiveringen av design editor chefer via deklarationen av en <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.SubscribeContextCallback>attribut i hanteraren för redigeraren design.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.SubscribeContextCallback> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ContextItemManager>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Activites.Design.ContextItemManager>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activites.Design.ContextItemManager>.</xref:System.Activites.Design.ContextItemManager>

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the service manager to be returned from the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.Services*> property.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en instans av service manager som ska returneras från den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.Services*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.Services*>

trans-unit.source: The default implementation creates a <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ServiceManager> that supports delayed activation of design editor managers through the declaration of a <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.SubscribeContextCallback> attribute on the design editor manager.
trans-unit.target: Standardimplementering skapar en <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ServiceManager>som stöder den fördröjda aktiveringen av design editor chefer via deklarationen av en <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.SubscribeContextCallback>attribut i hanteraren för redigeraren design.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.SubscribeContextCallback> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ServiceManager>

trans-unit.source: Returns the local collection of context items stored by the current editing context.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar lokal samling av kontexten objekt som lagras av den aktuella kontexten för redigering.

trans-unit.source: The Items collection is for data that is shared between a host and the designer.
trans-unit.target: Objektmängden är för data som delas mellan en värd och designer.

trans-unit.source: This data provides the mechanism needed to hook into subscription and change notification.
trans-unit.target: Dessa data innehåller den mekanism som behövs för att ansluta till prenumeration och ett meddelande om konfigurationsändring.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.ContextItemManager"></xref> collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.ContextItem"></xref> objects used in this editing context.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.ContextItemManager"> </xref> samling <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.ContextItem"> </xref> objekt som används i den här kontexten för redigering.

trans-unit.source: Returns the service manager used in the current editing context.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar service manager används i den aktuella kontexten för redigering.

trans-unit.source: Services represent functionality that is either provided by the host for the designer to use or that is used by the designer to make functionality available to all designers within the editor.
trans-unit.target: Tjänster representerar funktioner som tillhandahålls av värden för att använda antingen eller som används av designern tillgängliggöra funktioner till alla Designer i redigeraren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.ServiceManager"></xref> used in this editing context.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.ServiceManager"> </xref> användas i denna kontext för redigering.
